name: I am not making art. I just try to find a girlfriend.
description:
3D, Foto
2016
5697px x 3970px

The artist looks straight into our eyes – sad, fragile and thoughtful. The advert shows a man laughing and surrounded by females, they are consuming McDonald’s products. The fa-ces of females are covered with the distorted images of a heart and a car as if they artist considered them to be inaccessible. The sensitivity of the artist, underlined by the flowers he carries in his hand and a delicate golden necklace he is wearing, con-trasts with the self-confidence and superficiality of the alpha-man from the advert.
